{"_path":"/utils","_dir":"","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"工具","description":"使用组合式工具让你的服务器轻量且快速。","icon":"ph:function-bold","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"H3 是一个组合式框架。它不提供庞大的核心，而是从一个轻量的"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/guide/app"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"应用实例"}]},{"type":"text","value":"开始，对于每个功能，框架要么提供内置的工具，要么你可以自己创建。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与传统的插件/中间件方式相比，组合式工具具有巨大的优势："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"✅ 你的服务器只包含并运行所需的代码 "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✅ 你可以轻松扩展服务器功能，而无需添加全局插件 "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✅ 使用方式显式且简洁，减少了全局中间件和插件 "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所有工具都可以访问"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/guide/event"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"事件对象"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。这样它们可以访问传入请求并使用 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"event.context"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 共享上下文。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:2.utils:0.index.md","_source":"content","_file":"2.utils/0.index.md","_stem":"2.utils/0.index","_extension":"md"}